<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:14:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尽管特朗普推迟禁令，TikTok应用程序仍无法在美国苹果和谷歌商店上使用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-app-unavailable-apple-google-stores-us-despite-trump-delaying-ban-2025-01-21/</link><description>周二，TikTok 在美国的苹果和谷歌应用商店中仍然无法使用，一天前，唐纳德·特朗普总统签署了一项行政命令，将对这款流行的中国短视频应用程序的禁令的执行推迟 75 天。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:08:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-app-unavailable-apple-google-stores-us-despite-trump-delaying-ban-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>副总理表示中国不追求贸易顺差</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-is-not-seeking-trade-surplus-vice-premier-says-2025-01-21/</link><description>中国副总理丁薛祥周二表示，中国不追求贸易顺差，愿意进口更有竞争力的优质产品和服务来平衡贸易。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 13:27:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-is-not-seeking-trade-surplus-vice-premier-says-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>2024年中国非金融类对外直接投资同比增长10.5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-2024-non-financial-outbound-direct-investment-rose-105-year-2025-01-21/</link><description>中国商务部周二表示，按美元计算，2024年中国非金融类对外直接投资同比增长10.5%，达到1439亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 12:25:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-2024-non-financial-outbound-direct-investment-rose-105-year-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>四国外长在华盛顿举行会议，表明特朗普对中国的关注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-washington-signal-trumps-china-focus-2025-01-21/</link><description>美国国务卿马可·卢比奥将于周二开始行动，在唐纳德·特朗普总统开始第二个任期后的第二天，他将在华盛顿主持澳大利亚、印度和日本国务卿的会议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 12:04:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-washington-signal-trumps-china-focus-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>副总理表示中国不追求贸易顺差愿平衡贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stable-growth-strong-impetus-global-economy-vice-premier-says-2025-01-21/</link><description>中国副总理丁薛祥周二表示，中国不追求贸易顺差，愿意进口更有竞争力的优质产品和服务来平衡贸易。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 11:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stable-growth-strong-impetus-global-economy-vice-premier-says-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：“走走停停”特朗普关税贸易鞭打美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-21/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 11:07:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>中缅泰达成铲除电信诈骗中心共识</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-myanmar-thailand-reach-consensus-eradicate-telecom-fraud-centres-2025-01-21/</link><description>据中国国家广播电台报道，中国、缅甸、泰国官员周二在中国昆明举行会议，就消除缅甸电信诈骗中心达成共识。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 10:47:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-myanmar-thailand-reach-consensus-eradicate-telecom-fraud-centres-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>万科困境考验中国房地产业复苏努力的极限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/vanke-woes-test-limits-chinas-property-sector-revival-efforts-2025-01-21/</link><description>近年来，在采取了多项措施解决房地产市场的流动性危机之后，预计北京最终将重拾旧的做法，直接介入以稳定被视为该行业领头羊的国有开发商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 10:33:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/vanke-woes-test-limits-chinas-property-sector-revival-efforts-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>冯德莱恩在达沃斯演讲中表示欧盟愿意与美国合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/eus-von-der-leyen-says-need-work-together-avoid-global-race-bottom-2025-01-21/</link><description>特朗普表示，他希望通过关税或增加能源出口来扭转美国对欧盟的贸易逆差。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 10:13:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/eus-von-der-leyen-says-need-work-together-avoid-global-race-bottom-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>报告称，中国奢侈品市场进入“新常态”，预计 2025 年销量持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-enters-new-normal-luxury-market-with-flat-sales-expected-2025-report-says-2025-01-21/</link><description>咨询公司贝恩公司在发布最新《中国奢侈品报告》时表示，2024年中国奢侈品市场将下降18%至20%，标志着“指数增长”时期的结束，预计今年销售额将持平周二。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-enters-new-normal-luxury-market-with-flat-sales-expected-2025-report-says-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>泰国对中国游客免签政策因一系列犯罪行为而受到批评</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailands-visa-waiver-chinese-tourists-under-fire-after-string-crimes-2025-01-21/</link><description>在备受瞩目的中国演员绑架案和类似犯罪事件引发人们对旅游业和安全的担忧之后，泰国对中国公民的免签证计划受到了密切关注。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailands-visa-waiver-chinese-tourists-under-fire-after-string-crimes-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>习近平和普京讨论与特朗普、乌克兰和台湾的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-vows-further-develop-ties-with-xi-just-hours-after-trump-inauguration-2025-01-21/</link><description>弗拉基米尔·普京和习近平拥有广阔的世界观，认为随着中国在许多领域挑战美国的霸主地位，西方已经颓废和衰落。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:49:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-vows-further-develop-ties-with-xi-just-hours-after-trump-inauguration-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>德国汽车协会呼吁“经济实力”应对特朗普</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-auto-association-calls-economic-strength-face-trump-2025-01-21/</link><description>德国汽车协会主席周二表示，德国和欧洲需要变得更加独立和更具竞争力，以应对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普提出的挑战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:47:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-auto-association-calls-economic-strength-face-trump-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>普京告诉习近平，俄中关系在国际事务中发挥稳定作用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-china-ties-play-stabilising-role-international-affairs-putin-tells-xi-2025-01-21/</link><description>俄罗斯总统普京周二对中国国家主席习近平表示，莫斯科和北京的外交政策关系在国际事务中发挥了稳定作用。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:42:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-china-ties-play-stabilising-role-international-affairs-putin-tells-xi-2025-01-21/</guid></item><item><title>美银表示，投资者通过大量股票配置“让欧洲再次伟大”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/investors-make-europe-great-again-with-big-stock-allocation-bofa-says-2025-01-21/</link><description>美国银行全球研究部周二发布的一项投资者调查显示，随着落后的风险资产迎头赶上，欧洲股市在一月份出现了四分之一个世纪以来的第二大配置。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:23:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/investors-make-europe-great-again-with-big-stock-allocation-bofa-says-2025-01-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>